37117,cooking," This is the present state of the game
You are hungry! Let's cook a delicious meal. Check the cookbook in the kitchen for the recipe. Once done, enjoy your meal!
-= Kitchen =-
You've just walked into a kitchen.

You bend down to tie your shoe. When you stand up, you notice a fridge. The fridge is empty, what a horrible day! You make out an oven. Wow, isn't TextWorld just the best? You make out a table. On the table you can make out a cookbook. Now that's what I call TextWorld! You can make out a counter. On the counter you can make out a diced fried red potato, a red bell pepper and a raw yellow potato. You can't wait to tell the folks at home about this! You can see a stove. The stove is conventional. But the thing hasn't got anything on it.
